sentence: Cɛel aselkim-inek, trajuḍ kra n lweqt.
Agraw n Tigejda n Teqbaylit, ggten deg-s imeẓdaren d yimeɣnasen.
Ruḥent, meɛna, tasa-nsent ur tent-henna ara.
Ulamek ad nehder ɣef waya ma ulac later.
ama deg tɣerma ama deg yidles.
Fkiɣ-ak awal-iw ar ḥaca aḥraz ara k-ḥerzeɣ.
Ḥekkun ɣef urgaz tuɣeḍ, amzun d asalas.
Yeɣra deg uɣerbaz aɣelnaw n tsenselkimt, sakin yedda ar Franṣa anida ihegga tazrawt n Duktura.
Deggret-t ɣer tesga n umezruy, dinna kan i d amkan-is.
Taḥbult iγer ad ttmenγan γef lwert.
Ad yekker ula d ccix ad ixemmel ifassen-is.
Dakken tezmer ad d-tufrar deg yal taɣult.
Ɛahed-iyi ur as-tedliḍ i dduḥ ḥaca ma yettru-d uqcic.
Ittwarna deg kra n ismal akken ad isfuγel tirziwin inek , akken daγen ad d-yesken timahaltin am tqefalt n beṭṭu
Iεeqqayen i yuγalen d arekti, senγadent-ten, rennunt-asen kra n waman deg teswiεet γer tayeḍ.
Deg temssizzelt n tazzla tezga-d Zehra d tamzwarut.
Tilufa am tiyi ur nwiɣ ara ad iyi-d-teḍru i nekk.
Ur yi-d-ḥebbes ara mi ara d-ttmeslayeɣ.
Unuɣen urmiden mačči i imecṭaḥ kan ay mmugen.
D alef u xems meyya u ɛecra.
A yemma d lawan n lmut, dεu-yi a d-teqqel tefsut.
Yella yiwen n umkan isem-is Tizi.
